description: Lists tags for the specified resource.

parameters.name: ResourceARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource that you want to retrieve tags for.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: The tags that are assigned to the resource.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: The key identifier, or name, of the tag.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: The string value that's associated with the key of the tag. You can set the value of a tag to an empty string, but you can't set the value of a tag to null.
